const saltIsTurning25 = `<p>What a ride! What a journey! What a story! </p><p>The number 25 has significance beyond just being a number. It signifies Salt's beginning, our growth and our continued drive to live and deliver our values everywhere.&nbsp;</p><p>CHALLENGE - EMPOWER - IMPACT&nbsp;</p><p>All great things start with a visionary leader that has what it takes to give live to a dream. One step at a time, and sometimes with leaps and bounds.&nbsp;</p><p>Salt's humble beginnings in Namibia started when Logical Networks was formed in 1998 by the South African Datatec Group as a specialist network design, installation, commissioning, and maintenance company. The team driving things behind the scenes knew that there is more Salt can to for the Namibian economy through smarter technology, and that is when in 2008 the name changed to Salt. Without Salt, the ocean is just dam water. We are the ocean to your business.&nbsp;</p><p>Every entrepreneur, company founder and owner will tell you, that the first step is the scariest and most exhilarating at the same time. And any chef worth his/hers Salt will tell you, the perfect recipe comes through hard work, trials, and error, and a never give up attitude.&nbsp;</p><p>We love celebrating the small things as much as we love celebrating our 25th birthday. We love changing people's lives one technology at a time. We are more than technology enthusiasts; we are leaders in making a difference. We love what we do, we love to CHALLENGE, we love to EMPOWER, and we love to IMPACT.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>We love every day and every opportunity!&nbsp;</p><p>Salt would never have been here to celebrate this momentous occasion without the continued support from our customers, partners, distributors, and vendors and most of all, the Salties. You all have played such a crucial part in every success story we have to tell. There are not enough words to thank each one of you!&nbsp;</p><p>Here is to the next 25 years, and all our stakeholders continuing the journey with us!&nbsp;</p><h3> #impact #futurefit #empower #25</h3><figure><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/Articles/Sonja1.jpg" alt="" width="146" height="146"></figure><p>Sonja Coetzer - Managing Director</p>`;

